 patterns of activity in EHGs, which is a step forward towards\ndeveloping reliable, portable devices to reduce risks during pregnancy and\nlabor.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2022 02:25:20 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Feb 2023 16:40:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-28"}
