 into constraints on the [CII] halo\nluminosity-mass relation $L_\\mathrm{[CII]}(M)$ model parameters and the star\nformation rate density (SFRD) from [CII] emission. We also develop sensitivity\nestimates for CO, showing the ability to differentiate between models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 6 Sep 2022 13:41:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-05"}
